oil prices have leaped to the highest level of 
the year partly reflecting speculation that opec would be able to 
recruit help from outside producers to constrict world supplies 
on the new york mercantile exchange the maydelivery contract 
for west texas intermediate crude oil jumped 101 per barrel on 
